data.title: Zorro's black whip: Volume one
data.meta_description: The owner of the town's stagecoach line and a leading citizen, is opposed to Idaho becoming a state, and kills the proprietor of the town's newspaper for endorsing it. The editor's sister, an expert with a bullwhip and pistol, dons a black costume.
